ActPublic Service Employment Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Office of the Governor General's Secretary Employment Regulations
PrecisRegulations Amending THE OFFICE OF THE GOVERNOR GENERAL’S SECRETARY EMPLOYMENT REGULATIONS in order to replace the numbers of the eleven excluded positions at the Office of the Governor General’s Secretary (rendered obsolete by a move to a new electronic HR system) with new position numbers to ensure that the regulations continue to apply to these positions.
